P & G SAYS BUYS UNILEVER TEA UNIT . Plantation & General Investments Plc said on Wednesday it bought Sayama Tea Estates Ltd , the British holding company of Lujeri Tea Estates Ltd , from Unilever Plc for 2 . 8 million pounds . Lujeri is based in Southern Malawi and manufactures 4 . 7 million kilogrammes of tea annually at two factories , P & G said in a statement . - - Tony Roddam , London Newsroom + 44 171 542 4019 
